  <brief_title>Leucine Supplementation in Young Subjects Undergoing Resistance Training</brief_title>
  <sponsors>
    <lead_sponsor>
      <agency>University of Sao Paulo</agency>
      <agency_class>Other</agency_class>
    </lead_sponsor>
  </sponsors>
  <source>University of Sao Paulo</source>
  <oversight_info>
    <has_dmc>No</has_dmc>
  </oversight_info>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Leucine supplementation could be useful to support muscle anabolism. This study aims to
      investigate the effects of leucine supplementation on muscle mass and muscle strength in
      young subjects undergoing resistance training.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
